@BlytheRayne I'm scared of playing with colours because I'm shit at figuring out what colours go well with one another 😖

And I'm not good at drawing and my perfectionism would torture me if I make even a slight mistake 😭

But I totally agree that bullet is too rigid and boring for me!

@lilacnonsense I'm genuinely confused by this tweet 😅

I always whatsapp people because it's free? And supports emojis &amp; gifs? Nobody sends text messages anymore

And I'd be horrified if anyone called

@beegeehomemaker This tweet got me thinking 🤔 I don't naturally think of feelings words but want to use them often!

So what I do is open up the thesaurus, enter the closest generic word I can think of (e.g. excited) and find a synonym that best describes my feelings.

Is this... masking??

@ImStuckWithADHD Yes totally!! 💯

What I shared was what happens "for me".

I'm just sharing it for people who think I'm just a people pleaser and this behaviour has no correlation with ADHD or anxiety in any way.

@WhatTheADHD A deficit of the ability to control our impulses
&amp;
A deficit of the ability to control our focus

